  <name>Budgie Quicklaunch Applet</name>
  <summary>Simple applet to load executable files from a specified folder</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
    Budgie Quicklaunch Applet is an addon for Budgie Desktop to allow the quick execution of regular apps.
    </p>
    <p>
    These files must not be desktop files and must be executable.
    </p>
    <p>
    Features of the applet:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Folder Selection</li>
      <li>Notification</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
